Package com.skyhookwireless.accelerator

Interface Summary
AcceleratorClient.CampaignVisitsListener The listener for receiving campaign visit information.
AcceleratorClient.ConnectionCallbacks Provides callbacks that are called when the client is connected or disconnected from the service.
AcceleratorClient.IPLocationListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the request to determine location from IP address completes.
AcceleratorClient.NearbyMonitoredVenuesListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the operation to fetch nearby monitored venues completes.
AcceleratorClient.OnConnectionFailedListener Provides callbacks for scenarios that result in a failed attempt to connect the client to the service.
AcceleratorClient.OnPersonaResultListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the operation to refresh the demographic persona completes.
AcceleratorClient.OnRegisterForCampaignMonitoringResultListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the operation to register for campaign monitoring completes.
AcceleratorClient.OnStartCampaignMonitoringResultListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the operation to start monitoring campaigns completes.
AcceleratorClient.OnStopCampaignMonitoringResultListener The listener for receiving callbacks when the operation to stop monitoring campaigns completes.
AcceleratorClient.VenueInfoListener The listener for receiving venue information.
